{"tid":160047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路訊通去年虧損收窄　不再入標九巴巴士電視業務","createTime":"2017-03-17T12:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T15:50:25.000Z","uid":48093,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88cfddbc5ce673908d5349e22f6017aff0e642a7","tid":160047,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"路訊通去年虧損4530萬元，縮窄逾半成，業績虧損主要由於市場需求持續疲弱令收入減少、人民幣貶值導致匯兌虧損950萬元、就物業、廠房及設備確認減值虧損2290萬元，以及為巴士電視業務虧損合約撥備1450萬元。不派末期息。<br />\n<br />\n公司去年總收入4.15億元，下跌3.5%。<br />\n<br />\n路訊通表示，考慮過九巴巴士電視業務新特許權招標條款後，決定不會遞交新標書。現有特許權今年6月底屆滿。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，九巴已行使選擇權，將巴士車身及巴士車廂廣告業務的特許協議年期延長36個月，直至2020年6月底。特許協議所有其他條款及條件維持不變。"},{"pid":"df6281fa50e8c5790e9bdb5fceacbcb2fdbc0bff","tid":160047,"uid":69148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:08:23.000Z","msg":"終於收皮，太好哼啦"},{"pid":"10c635aa9d6c9d9ca420d881848bfc7669fc1ba7","tid":160047,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"以後唔駛再聽便便同口嗅"},{"pid":"e0ef9994a702d39ad095fbee4f2da0a6ad16ebf7","tid":160047,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"個moon報下站都好過播野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a88f1aaa1c679a4d4d6f1ee9e263998b5eefcc","tid":160047,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"另一方面，九巴已行使選擇權，將巴士車身及巴士車廂廣告業務的特許協議年期延長36個月，直至2020年6月底。<br />\n<br />\n2020"},{"pid":"88c1367fdef640f68c6e8d6b2a2e2a14daae6b4e","tid":160047,"uid":18309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"Gaia oh gaia, thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfd2e3117bc0d9779a23161276b19185a0db0040","tid":160047,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Gaia oh gaia, thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil